summary: I have 15+ years professional experience in international account management (SaaS), Sales, Marketing and Business Development. I have worked in start-ups, in a large corporate and even as an entrepreneur. I thrive in an international setting, speaking several languages - often within the same sentence! I am happiest working with a diverse, dynamic team. I enjoy influencing and building relationships with colleagues and clients. What I do best? Creating a seamless customer journey. That and cooking.
